Yemaneberhan "Yeman" Crippa (amụrụ na 15 Ọktoba n'afọ 1996) bụ onye Ịtali a mụrụ na Etiopia
Onye ritere ihe nrite ọla edo na 2019 European Team Championships (5000 m) na 2019 European 10,000m Cup
O sonyere na 2020 Summer Olympics, na 5000 m, na 10000 m.

N'ọkwa ndị ntorobịa, o ritere ihe nrite ọla edo na 2017 European Athletics U23 Championships na n'ọsọ ndị na-erubeghị afọ 20 na 2014 na 2015 European Cross Country Championships na ọla nchara na asọmupi U23 na 2016 European Cross Country Championship.
A mụrụ ya na Dessie, n'akụkụ ugwu ọwụwa anyanwụ nke Etiopia, Yemaneberhan tụfuru nne na nna ya ndị Etiopia na Agha Eritrea ma daa n'ụlọ ụmụ mgbei na Addis Abeba
Di na nwunye ndị Ịtali, Roberto na Luisa Crippa, kuchiri ya n'afọ 2001 ma soro ha biri na Trento
Ọ bụ otu n'ime ụmụ itoolu di na nwunye ahụ kuchiri, ya na ụmụnne ya ndị okenye Nekagenet na Kelemu
Na mbido, o lekwasịrị anya na bọọlụ tupu ọ gbanwee gaa na ịgba ọsọ na 2007, ụmụnne ya abụọ bụkwa ndị na-agba ọsọ.
Na erimeri ọtụtụ ihe nrite n'ụdị afọ dị iche iche, o mere nke mbụ ya na 2016 European Championships na Amsterdam na-emecha nke asatọ na mita 5000
Otu afọ mgbe nke ahụ gasịrị, ọ mechara nke asaa na mita 3000 na 2017 European Indoor Championships na Belgrade.
N'afọ 2019, o mere ihe ndekọ mba 10,000 mita na Doha World Championship na 27:10.76.
